One Move Captures Black (21)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to Play.\b0
\par Black's eyespace is narrow but it is still not easy to kill.
\par
\par If you can solve this problem without making any mistakes, you are most likely stronger than 8k.
\par }
