Diagram 2 (Alive)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White's dansu from the outside with 1 lets black live. Black 2 is the vital point for life.
\par
\par Where should white play then? There is only one place white can play.
\par }
